_props.Name: Apollo's Propital
_props.Description: With Apollo's Propital coursing through your veins, you'll remain in the fight for a longer period of time.

_props.Name: Apollo's CMS
_props.ShortName: Not even 100 Blackened limbs can stop the god of war!

_props.Name: Armor of Athena
_props.Description: The Armor Of Athena provides the highest level of protection for all your common body parts. A bit on the heavy side (this was worn by a god after all) you might want to couple it with the Helmet of Hermes.

_props.Name: Atlas' Satchel
_props.Description: With Atlas' Satchel, you feel like you could carry the world on your back.

_props.Name: Hercules' Rig
_props.Description: If heroic labors didn't stop him, what makes you think a little weight matters?

_props.Name: Hercules' Rig 2
_props.Description: All of his strength, and now all of his protection.

_props.Name: Helmet Of Hermes
_props.Description: The Helmet of Hermes protects your entire head while also making you feel light on your feet.
